### Disable NestJS Body Parser for Better Auth

Source: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/canary/docs/content/docs/integrations/nestjs.mdx

Configure the NestJS application to disable its built-in body parser. This is a critical step that allows Better Auth to correctly process the raw request body, ensuring proper functionality and avoiding conflicts.

```ts
import { NestFactory } from "@nestjs/core";
import { AppModule } from "./app.module";

async function bootstrap() {
  const app = await NestFactory.create(AppModule, {
    bodyParser: false, // Required for Better Auth
  });
  await app.listen(process.env.PORT ?? 3000);
}
bootstrap();
```

